body_html:
Hi, verified. With Android Studio 3.1 (Canary) it's easier to see method runtime.
For commit 1b960c3 (1 before move to Java): runInference took 6ms, fillNodeFloat took <1ms
For commit 1a9769d: runInference took 6ms, fillNodeFloat took 49ms.

Most of the time goes on Tensor.create(). Relevant line:

        t.buffer().asFloatBuffer().put(data);

body:
Hi, verified. With Android Studio 3.1 (Canary) it's easier to see method runtime.
For commit 1b960c30ab (1 before move to Java): `runInference` took 6ms, `fillNodeFloat` took <1ms
For commit 1a9769dc79fdd27c347633df210ff64f48de8d07: `runInference` took 6ms, `fillNodeFloat` took 49ms.

Most of the time goes on `Tensor.create()`. Relevant line:
```
        t.buffer().asFloatBuffer().put(data);
```
